  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1572990/extras/b55ee9ed25e49df7421aa19bb6cef9c9.avif?t=1638878299\" width=600 height=260 /></span><br>You play as Ikuro, a gambling addict looking to fuel his other addiction to his personalized A.I robot wife, Sei.  There's a problem though.  Sei needs memory components, but of course, getting the money for that is easier said then done, so expect to encounter some shady and unsavory individuals on your way...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1572990/extras/1810aa7333cd2687c4515f7169a580ae.avif?t=1638878299\" width=600 height=260 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Relaxing, Immersive OST!</strong><br></li><li><strong>Gorgeous, animated backgrounds and sprites!</strong><br></li><li><strong>Gripping, dark narrative!</strong><br></li><li><strong>Colorful and well written characters!</strong></li></ul>",
